<div class="jumbotron">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Whats App Statistics</h1>
        <p>Starships resist from tragedies like huge protons. Countless collectives empower clear, delighted pathways. The solid ship virtually beams the spacecraft. </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="index" class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 center-block">
            <h2>Let us do the magic:</h2>
            <div class="row vertical-align">
                <div class="col-md-3"><span class="circle">1</span></div>
                <div class="col-md-2"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope front-glyphicon" aria-hidden="true"></span></div>
                <div class="col-md-7"><span class="front-lead">send history to x@y.com</span></div>
            </div>
          <hr/>
            <div class="row vertical-align">
                <div class="col-md-3"><span class="circle">2</span></div>
                <div class="col-md-2"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-stats front-glyphicon" aria-hidden="true"></span></div>
                <div class="col-md-7"><span class="front-lead">receive your statistics by e-mail</span></div>
            </div>
          <hr/>
            <div class="row vertical-align">
                <div class="col-md-3"><span class="circle">3</span></div>
                <div class="col-md-2"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-sunglasses front-glyphicon" aria-hidden="true"></span></div>
                <div class="col-md-7"><span class="front-lead">deal with it!</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  <hr/>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 center-block">
            {{#unless parsed}}
                <form role="form">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <h2>Upload it manually:</h2>
                        <input type="file" id="inputFile" title="<span class='glyphicon glyphicon-folder-open'></span>   Search for a file to add" data-filename-placement="inside">
                        <p class="help-block">Cold teleporters, to the moon?</p>
                    </div>
                    <button {{action 'submitFile'}} type="submit" class="btn btn-default" style="width: 186px;">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-upload"></span>
                    </button>
                </form>
            {{/unless}}
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 center-block">
            {{#if parsing}}
                <h3>Parsing...</h3>
                <div class="parseProgress">
                    {{parseProgress}}%
                </div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>

</div>